        "created_at": "2018-10-24T07:01:44.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hello, I am French then excuse I for the English translation. I am a fan of LBA 1 and 2 for a long time and I had the opportunity to test LBA 1 enhanced Edition  at a friend. It is a real present, a handiness, a zoom, a picture of the jumps and the shootings,playable in the lever, brilliant!<br>\nI shall like knowing if LBA 2 also benefits from these improvements, because in other articles that speaks about classic LBA2 version and I already have the original. If somebody had the opportunity to make out a will I shall like his opinion. Thank you in advance.<img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
